<HEADLINE> Coulthard Fined 5,000 Dollars For Speeding </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, July 12 (Xinhua) -- Scotish driver David Coulthard was
fined 5,000 U.S. dollars for speeding in the pit lane during the
qualifying session for the British Formula One Grand Prix in
Silverstone on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Coulthard, behind the wheels of Mclaren Mercedes, clocked 93.2
kmh, well over the 80 kmh pit lane speed limit. 
</P>
