prepared for the World Horticulture Fair, to be held in Kunming,
from May 10 to October 31, 1999.
</P>
<P>
Li, who is the head of the fair's organizing committee, said
that this is a good chance for international exchanges and
cooperation and to display China's achievements in environmental
protection.
</P>
<P>
