government, and the last large international event before the new
century, noted Li who is also a member of the Political Bureau of
the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China.
</P>
<P>
"China should use the chance to describe its abundant
horticultural and gardening resources and to show the Chinese
government's determination to increase environmental protection
and better polish China's international image," Li said.
</P>
<P>
"As the host of the fair, Yunnan can also increase its
opening-up and better explore its rich tourist and biological
resources," he said.
</P>
<P>
Li visited the construction site of various halls and buildings
for the fair and urged central and local governments to continue
their support for the event.  
