<HEADLINE> Media Card Locations Set for Bangkok Asian Games </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, July 13 (Xinhua) -- The organizing committee of
the 13th Asian Games has designated four locations to issue
identification cards to media members who will cover the
event scheduled for December 6-20 next year in Bangkok.
</P>
