open two main press centers for the Games, one at the sports
complex of Thammasat University and another at Muangthong Thani
sports complex three months before the event takes place.
</P>
<P>
The subcommittee also plans to launch questionnaire surveys
in October this year and June next year respectively to assess
the media's needs for facilities.
</P>
<P>
It is requiring assitance from volunteers and foreign
embassies to help carry out tasks during the Games.  
</P>
</TEXT>
