<HEADLINE> Israel to Toughen Crackdown on Palestinian </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, July 13 (Xinhua) -- The Israeli military authorities
has decided to tighten the screws against Palestinian resistance,
the state-run Israel Radio reported today.
</P>
<P>
